      <symbol code="116" id="14" name="Pit" type="1">
        <description>A pit or hole with distinct steep sides which cannot be represented to scale with the symbol earth bank (106). The minimum diameter shall be 2 m. The minimum depth from the surrounding ground shall be 1 m. The symbol is orientated to north.</description>
